Comments #1: Radiocarbon dates affected by reservoir effect. According to Van Zeist (2009), the radiocarbon dates are not reliable, even with the correction for the reservoir effect. They opted for a chronology based on the correlation with other biostratigraphic records. Thus, we have followed their recommendations.
